OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F332A1782125278
OL,3,CMan, 34, dies after motorcycle crash
OL,4,Con A19
OL,6,FNorth Yorkshire Police are appealing
OL,7,Ffor information following the death of
OL,8,Fa motorcyclist following a collision
OL,9,Fon the A19 in North Yorkshire.
OL,11,FThe incident occurred at approximately
OL,12,F1:50pm, on Friday, 19 June, just north
OL,13,Fof Chapel Haddlesey. It involved a
OL,14,Fblack Honda motorcycle and a red
OL,15,FVauxhall Corsa.
OL,17,FThe rider of the motorcycle, a 34-year-
OL,18,Fold man from the Selby area, was taken
OL,19,Fto hospital where he later died.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/3
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
